msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.astype"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.astype:1 of
msgid "Cast a pandas object to a specified dtype ``dtype``."
msgstr "将 pandas 对象转换为指定的 dtype ``dtype``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.astype of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.astype:3 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Use a numpy.dtype or Python type to cast entire pandas object to the same"
" type. Alternatively, use {col: dtype, ...}, where col is a column label "
"and dtype is a numpy.dtype or Python type to cast one or more of the "
"DataFrame's columns to column-specific types."
msgstr ""
"使用 numpy.dtype 或 Python 类型将整个 pandas 对象转换为相同类型。或者使用"
" {col: dtype, ...}，其中 col 是列标签，dtype 是 numpy.dtype 或 Python "
"类型，用于将 DataFrame 的一列或多列转换为特定列类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.astype:8 of
msgid ""
"Return a copy when ``copy=True`` (be very careful setting ``copy=False`` "
"as changes to values then may propagate to other pandas objects)."
msgstr ""
"当 ``copy=True`` 时返回副本（设置 ``copy=False`` 时要非常小心，因为值的"
"更改可能会传播到其他 pandas 对象）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.astype:12 of
msgid ""
"Control raising of exceptions on invalid data for provided dtype.  - "
"``raise`` : allow exceptions to be raised - ``ignore`` : suppress "
"exceptions. On error return original object."
msgstr ""
"控制在提供的 dtype 数据无效时是否引发异常。- ``raise``：允许引发异常 - ``"
"ignore``：抑制异常。出错时返回原始对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.astype:12 of
msgid "Control raising of exceptions on invalid data for provided dtype."
msgstr "控制对提供的数据类型中无效数据引发异常。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.astype:14 of
msgid "``raise`` : allow exceptions to be raised"
msgstr "``raise`` : 允许引发异常"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.astype:15 of
msgid "``ignore`` : suppress exceptions. On error return original object."
msgstr "``ignore`` : 抑制异常。出错时返回原始对象。"

